text_raw:
2. The 13th day of December 2023 is appointed as the day on which the 
Agricultural and Food Supply Chain Act 2023 (No. 19 of 2023) shall come into 
operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

12 December, 2023. 

CHARLIE MCCONALOGUE, 

Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 15th December, 2023.
